&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
	&lt;ol&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;What is the purpose of the change&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ol&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;


&lt;p&gt;    With this PR the spotbugs plugin can now be run on a single sub-module. The path to the exclusion file is now absolute and no longer relies on in which module it is executed.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
	&lt;ol&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Verifying this change&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ol&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;


&lt;p&gt;    Run &lt;tt&gt;mvn package -Dspotbugs&lt;/tt&gt; in any sub-module.&lt;/p&gt;


